text: Claudia Hernández Aguila (born 9 January 1997) is a Cuban volleyball player. She played at the 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2017 FIVB U23 Volleyball Women's World Championship, and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship.
